Carl Froch 's dream of a fight in Las Vegas against Julio Cesar Chavez Jr looks to have gone up in smoke after the former middleweight world champion was stopped in nine rounds by Andrzej Fonfara .
Froch has said he may retire if that fight does not come to fruition .
The 37-year-old super-middleweight , has not fought since George Groves at Wembley Stadium .